                   in proof generation. Experiments demonstrate that our method
                   improves proof success rates by 2.05\% on miniF2F and 1.69\%
                   on ProofNet while reducing proof complexity by 23.81\% and
                   16.50\% respectively. The code is available at
                   https://github.com/Car-pe/HAGBP.},
