                   ($\sim$8\%$\uparrow$), OlympiadBench ($\sim$4\%$\uparrow$),
                   DocFinQA ($\sim$7\%$\uparrow$), and GPQA
                   ($\sim$1\%$\uparrow$). Our key finding highlights that
                   constraint-guided iterative verification improves
