               experimental modalities. Here we critically evaluate these
               modeling attempts, highlighting the continued need to reconcile
               the array of disparate ACC observations within a coherent,
               unifying framework.},
	author = {Vassena, Eliana and Holroyd, Clay B and Alexander, William H},
	journal = {Front. Neurosci.},
	keywords = {anterior cingulate cortex (ACC); computational modeling; computational models of ACC; effort; effortful control; prediction error},
