              exact number concepts unclear. Here, we return to this question by
              replicating methods previously used to assess exact number
              knowledge in innumerate groups, such as the Piraha, with a large
              sample of semi- numerate US toddlers. We replicate previous
              findings from both innumerate cultures and developmental studies
